						<div class="postbody">SMB1 uses a 32x13-metatile sliding window, divided into a 16x13 array for nametable $2000 and a 16x13 array for nametable $2400.<br /><br />My current project uses a 32x24-byte array because it doesn't scroll (sorry, tokumaru) and there are 24 rows of 30 8x8 pixel cells.</div>

